name: The San Fran necklace
description:
Punk rock with a decidedly feminine touch.  Varying silver chains, assymetrically arranged. 

Approximately 17” at shortest point, 21” at longest point.  Extendable length to 2” with lobster clasp.

name: The Santa Monica necklace
description:
Blur the cultural lines and travel without going anywhere.  This necklace will make you feel like you're on vacation, yet right at home.

Tiny, sea-colored seed beads, chunky white jasper and rare Himalayan red coral beads evoke the sea.  Sterling silver chain and details add a touch of shine to complement Nature's beauty.
  
Approximate length 26” with a 3” drop.  The length is adjustable up to 2".

name: The Wooly Bracelet
description:
We've updated one of our favorite pieces to suit you better!  
With a bit of shine, a lot of style and a fuzzy feel, you'll want to wear this bracelet for days.  And now with a new anti-tarnish clasp and a lower price, there are more reasons to love the Wooly than it's good looks.

Handmade of limited edition Japanese fiber, this bracelet exudes the toughness of a cuff with its tender wooly underside.   6.5” long with a silver plated, tarnish-resistant brass clasp.

name: The Kona necklace
description:
Let that Earth goddess in you shine through.  Petrified wood beads from the Himalayan mountains form a unique base.  Brilliant turquoise Czech glass and pure white jasper beads brightly illuminate your neckline.  The result: A piece that looks as good as it feels to wear.  Your skin deserves it. 

The four strands of beads are finished off at the back of the neck with beautifully hand-hammered sterling silver Thai cones.  Approximate length 23” with a 3” drop.  The length is extendable up to 2”.  All silver components are 100% sterling silver.

name: The Taos necklace
description:
Layers of texture create a delicate tapestry of beads, silver and bronze.  Rich colors and warm tones create an piece fit for royalty.  Pair with a billowy top or a simple neckline.  Whatever you wear it with, get ready to walk with an extra strut in your step.  

This necklace is finished off at the back of the neck with hand-hammered, sterling silver Thai cones. Approximate length 26” and is extendable by 2".

name: The J Bracelet
description:
Variations on a theme of gold.  A decadent play of textures, sizes and shapes compose this versatile and eye-catching bracelet.  

Made of tarnish resistant and hypoallergenic gold filled links.  Length 6-3/4” including magnetic barrel clasp.

name: The Grace Earrings
description:
Grecian-inspired rectangular windows of silver.  Shimmering oval drops sway in the wind.  Perfectly paired with the Grace necklace, yet it stands alone beautifully.  Sensuous and architectural, these earrings complement short and long hair alike.

1 3/4" long and 1/2" wide.  All parts are 100% sterling silver.

name: The Grace necklace
description:
Drapes in three of sterling silver strands.  Equally beautiful with that sexy black dress or your favorite jeans.  Graceful indeed.
  
Approximate length 18” with 2” drop.  Extendable length to 2” with lobster clasp.

name: The Athena necklace
description:
Featuring shimmering, faceted quartz in shades of mauves and taupes, The Athena takes it cue from Greek antiquity.  Long, flattened ovals of sterling silver flow down the neckline.  Accentuating a woman's curves, it depicts a goddess' strength with subtlety as well.  

At 31" long, this piece is much longer than is pictured.  This is a piece the moves as you do, blends with you.  Destined to become a favorite, The Athena is one to span the generations.

The length is adjustable up to 2".

name: The Mina necklace
description:
With a nod to Byzatium's intricate breastplates and chain mail, the Mina features a more feminine approach to toughness.  Adorned with a singular, faceted Peruvian opal the color of the sea, this is no mere war armor.  Each piece is individually hand-hammered and formed, and designed to enhance your own natural, beautiful breastplate.

At 18” with a 2” extender, please feel free to convo me for a longer length as each piece is made to order.  The lobster clasp and all metal parts are 100% sterling silver.

name: The Maxine necklace
description:
A stunning single agate horn takes its place nestled among faceted milky quartz.  People are sure to notice this piece and want a second look.  Or a third, or fourth, or fifth...

Suspended on a 21” sterling silver chain that brings a modern touch to the earthy stones.  Extendable up to 3” with a lobster clasp.  All metal parts are 100% sterling silver.

name: The G Bracelet
description:
Airy bubbles of silver contrast with tight, tiny links to create a bit of contrasting drama.  5 strands of chain are unified with a sensual hook and chain.

Sterling silver.  Approximate length 5 1/4” without hook and chain clasp.  Extendable length up to 2”.
